dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Duytsche Mylen."
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Decorative cartouche, compass rose, rhumb lines.
Appears in Valentijn's Oud en Nieuw Oost-Indien, Dordrecht, 1724-1726.
